CREATE TABLE schema_version( ver_timestamp TIMESTAMP PRIMARY KEY, ver_versionstring VARCHAR(128) DEFAULT '$Revision: 1.1 $ $Date: 2009/06/09 11:13:09 $', ver_schema VARCHAR(16) DEFAULT '3_0' )

CREATE TABLE subscriber ( scr_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, scr_userid VARCHAR(256) NOT NULL, dev_identifier INT8 DEFAULT 0, scr_device_profile_diff TEXT, CONSTRAINT pk_scr_identifier PRIMARY KEY(scr_identifier), CONSTRAINT uc_subscriber UNIQUE(scr_userid) )

CREATE TABLE subscriber_attributes ( scr_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, scr_attributename VARCHAR(2048) NOT NULL, scr_attributevalue VARCHAR(4000), CONSTRAINT pk_subscriber_attributes PRIMARY KEY(scr_identifier, scr_attributename) )
ALTER TABLE subscriber_attributes ADD CONSTRAINT fk_subscriber_attributes FOREIGN KEY (scr_identifier) REFERENCES subscriber(scr_identifier)
CREATE INDEX idx_subscriber_attributes_name_value on subscriber_attributes(scr_attributename,scr_attributevalue)

CREATE TABLE subscriber_group ( scg_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, scg_name VARCHAR(128) NOT NULL, CONSTRAINT pk_subscriber_group1 PRIMARY KEY(scg_identifier), CONSTRAINT uc_subscriber_group1 UNIQUE(scg_name) )
COMMENT ON TABLE subscriber_group is 'List of defined subscriber groups and their description'
COMMENT ON COLUMN subscriber_group.scg_identifier IS 'Unique Identifier for this group'
COMMENT ON COLUMN subscriber_group.scg_name IS ' Name for the Group ("Bronze", "adult", "WSJsubscribers")'

CREATE TABLE subscriber_group_attributes ( scg_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, scg_attributename VARCHAR(2048) NOT NULL, scg_attributevalue VARCHAR(4000), CONSTRAINT pk_subscriber_group_attributes PRIMARY KEY(scg_identifier, scg_attributename) )
ALTER TABLE subscriber_group_attributes ADD CONSTRAINT fk_subscriber_group_attributes FOREIGN KEY (scg_identifier) REFERENCES subscriber_group(scg_identifier)
CREATE INDEX idx_subscriber_group_attributes on subscriber_group_attributes(scg_attributevalue)

CREATE TABLE subscriber_group_members ( scg_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, grp_expires TIMESTAMP, grp_activeflag CHAR(1) DEFAULT '1', scr_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, CONSTRAINT pk_subscriber_group_members PRIMARY KEY (scg_identifier, scr_identifier), CONSTRAINT ck_subscriber_group_members CHECK (grp_activeflag in ('0','1')) )
CREATE INDEX idx_subscriber_group_members on subscriber_group_members(scr_identifier)
COMMENT ON TABLE subscriber_group_members IS 'A subscriber is in different groups. Group membership may be time-limited.'

CREATE TABLE device ( dev_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, dev_profile_url VARCHAR(3000) NOT NULL, dev_profile TEXT, dev_user_agent VARCHAR(256), dev_last_update TIMESTAMP, CONSTRAINT pk_dev_identifier PRIMARY KEY(dev_identifier) )
COMMENT ON TABLE device IS 'A mobile device'
COMMENT ON COLUMN device.dev_identifier IS 'a unique assigned number for the device'
COMMENT ON COLUMN device.dev_profile_url IS 'the device profile URL associated with the device'
COMMENT ON COLUMN device.dev_profile IS 'the cached XML profile retrieved from the dev_profile_url'
COMMENT ON COLUMN device.dev_user_agent IS 'the user-agent header string associated with the device'
COMMENT ON COLUMN device.dev_last_update IS 'the timestamp the profile data was last retrieved from the DEV_PROFILE_URL'
CREATE UNIQUE INDEX idx_dev_user_agent ON device (dev_user_agent)
CREATE TABLE community ( com_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, com_name VARCHAR(256) NOT NULL, CONSTRAINT pk_com_identifier PRIMARY KEY(com_identifier), CONSTRAINT uc_com_name UNIQUE(com_name) )
CREATE TABLE community_members ( com_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, scr_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, name VARCHAR(256), CONSTRAINT pk_community_members PRIMARY KEY(com_identifier, scr_identifier) )

CREATE TABLE community_admins ( com_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, scr_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, wantsaudit BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE, wantsnotifications BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE, name VARCHAR(256), CONSTRAINT pk_admins PRIMARY KEY(com_identifier, scr_identifier) )

CREATE TABLE subscriber_audit ( scr_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, aud_timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL, scr_userid VARCHAR(256) NOT NULL, aud_target VARCHAR(1024) NOT NULL, aud_reason VARCHAR(256) NOT NULL, aud_category VARCHAR(256), CONSTRAINT pk_aud_scr_identifier PRIMARY KEY(scr_identifier, aud_timestamp) )
CREATE TABLE subscriber_scheme ( scrsc_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, scr_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, sub_scheme INT4 DEFAULT '0' NOT NULL, CONSTRAINT pk_subscriber_scheme PRIMARY KEY(scrsc_identifier) )
COMMENT ON TABLE subscriber_scheme IS 'List of schemes for subscribers.'
COMMENT ON COLUMN subscriber_scheme.scrsc_identifier IS 'Unique Identifier for this subscriber scheme.'
COMMENT ON COLUMN subscriber_scheme.scr_identifier IS 'Identifier of subscriber.'
COMMENT ON COLUMN subscriber_scheme.sub_scheme IS 'Indicates whether scheme is "default", "none" or "custom".'
CREATE TABLE community_scheme ( comsc_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, com_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, com_scheme INT4 DEFAULT '0' NOT NULL, CONSTRAINT pk_community_scheme PRIMARY KEY(comsc_identifier) )
COMMENT ON TABLE community_scheme IS 'List of schemes for communities.'
COMMENT ON COLUMN community_scheme.comsc_identifier IS 'Unique Identifier for this community scheme.'
COMMENT ON COLUMN community_scheme.com_identifier IS 'Identifier of community'
COMMENT ON COLUMN community_scheme.com_scheme IS 'Indicates whether scheme is "default", "none" or "custom".'

CREATE TABLE subscriber_blocked_cats ( scrct_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, scr_identifier INT8 DEFAULT '0' NOT NULL, scr_category VARCHAR(128) NOT NULL, CONSTRAINT pk_subscriber_cats PRIMARY KEY(scrct_identifier) )

CREATE TABLE community_blocked_cats ( comct_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, com_identifier INT8 DEFAULT '0' NOT NULL, com_category VARCHAR(128) NOT NULL, CONSTRAINT pk_community_blocked_cats PRIMARY KEY(comct_identifier) )

CREATE TABLE subscriber_services ( scrse_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, scr_identifier INT8 DEFAULT '0' NOT NULL, ss_target_type VARCHAR(128), ss_target_url_sc VARCHAR(128), ss_target_sc_keyword VARCHAR(128), ss_block BOOLEAN DEFAULT TRUE, CONSTRAINT pk_subscriber_services PRIMARY KEY(scrse_identifier) )

CREATE TABLE schema_version( ver_timestamp TIMESTAMP PRIMARY KEY, ver_versionstring VARCHAR(128) DEFAULT '$Revision: 1.1 $ $Date: 2009/06/09 11:13:09 $', ver_schema VARCHAR(16) DEFAULT '3_0' )

CREATE TABLE subscriber ( scr_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, scr_userid VARCHAR(256) NOT NULL, dev_identifier INT8 DEFAULT 0, scr_device_profile_diff TEXT, CONSTRAINT pk_scr_identifier PRIMARY KEY(scr_identifier), CONSTRAINT uc_subscriber UNIQUE(scr_userid) )

CREATE TABLE subscriber_attributes ( scr_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, scr_attributename VARCHAR(2048) NOT NULL, scr_attributevalue VARCHAR(4000), CONSTRAINT pk_subscriber_attributes PRIMARY KEY(scr_identifier, scr_attributename) )
ALTER TABLE subscriber_attributes ADD CONSTRAINT fk_subscriber_attributes FOREIGN KEY (scr_identifier) REFERENCES subscriber(scr_identifier)
CREATE INDEX idx_subscriber_attributes_name_value on subscriber_attributes(scr_attributename,scr_attributevalue)

CREATE TABLE subscriber_group ( scg_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, scg_name VARCHAR(128) NOT NULL, CONSTRAINT pk_subscriber_group1 PRIMARY KEY(scg_identifier), CONSTRAINT uc_subscriber_group1 UNIQUE(scg_name) )
COMMENT ON TABLE subscriber_group is 'List of defined subscriber groups and their description'
COMMENT ON COLUMN subscriber_group.scg_identifier IS 'Unique Identifier for this group'
COMMENT ON COLUMN subscriber_group.scg_name IS ' Name for the Group ("Bronze", "adult", "WSJsubscribers")'

CREATE TABLE subscriber_group_attributes ( scg_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, scg_attributename VARCHAR(2048) NOT NULL, scg_attributevalue VARCHAR(4000), CONSTRAINT pk_subscriber_group_attributes PRIMARY KEY(scg_identifier, scg_attributename) )
ALTER TABLE subscriber_group_attributes ADD CONSTRAINT fk_subscriber_group_attributes FOREIGN KEY (scg_identifier) REFERENCES subscriber_group(scg_identifier)
CREATE INDEX idx_subscriber_group_attributes on subscriber_group_attributes(scg_attributevalue)

CREATE TABLE subscriber_group_members ( scg_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, grp_expires TIMESTAMP, grp_activeflag CHAR(1) DEFAULT '1', scr_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, CONSTRAINT pk_subscriber_group_members PRIMARY KEY (scg_identifier, scr_identifier), CONSTRAINT ck_subscriber_group_members CHECK (grp_activeflag in ('0','1')) )
CREATE INDEX idx_subscriber_group_members on subscriber_group_members(scr_identifier)
COMMENT ON TABLE subscriber_group_members IS 'A subscriber is in different groups. Group membership may be time-limited.'

CREATE TABLE device ( dev_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, dev_profile_url VARCHAR(3000) NOT NULL, dev_profile TEXT, dev_user_agent VARCHAR(256), dev_last_update TIMESTAMP, CONSTRAINT pk_dev_identifier PRIMARY KEY(dev_identifier) )
COMMENT ON TABLE device IS 'A mobile device'
COMMENT ON COLUMN device.dev_identifier IS 'a unique assigned number for the device'
COMMENT ON COLUMN device.dev_profile_url IS 'the device profile URL associated with the device'
COMMENT ON COLUMN device.dev_profile IS 'the cached XML profile retrieved from the dev_profile_url'
COMMENT ON COLUMN device.dev_user_agent IS 'the user-agent header string associated with the device'
COMMENT ON COLUMN device.dev_last_update IS 'the timestamp the profile data was last retrieved from the DEV_PROFILE_URL'
CREATE UNIQUE INDEX idx_dev_user_agent ON device (dev_user_agent)
CREATE TABLE community ( com_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, com_name VARCHAR(256) NOT NULL, CONSTRAINT pk_com_identifier PRIMARY KEY(com_identifier), CONSTRAINT uc_com_name UNIQUE(com_name) )
CREATE TABLE community_members ( com_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, scr_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, name VARCHAR(256), CONSTRAINT pk_community_members PRIMARY KEY(com_identifier, scr_identifier) )

CREATE TABLE community_admins ( com_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, scr_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, wantsaudit BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE, wantsnotifications BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE, name VARCHAR(256), CONSTRAINT pk_admins PRIMARY KEY(com_identifier, scr_identifier) )

CREATE TABLE subscriber_audit ( scr_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, aud_timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL, scr_userid VARCHAR(256) NOT NULL, aud_target VARCHAR(1024) NOT NULL, aud_reason VARCHAR(256) NOT NULL, aud_category VARCHAR(256), CONSTRAINT pk_aud_scr_identifier PRIMARY KEY(scr_identifier, aud_timestamp) )
CREATE TABLE subscriber_scheme ( scrsc_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, scr_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, sub_scheme INT4 DEFAULT '0' NOT NULL, CONSTRAINT pk_subscriber_scheme PRIMARY KEY(scrsc_identifier) )
COMMENT ON TABLE subscriber_scheme IS 'List of schemes for subscribers.'
COMMENT ON COLUMN subscriber_scheme.scrsc_identifier IS 'Unique Identifier for this subscriber scheme.'
COMMENT ON COLUMN subscriber_scheme.scr_identifier IS 'Identifier of subscriber.'
COMMENT ON COLUMN subscriber_scheme.sub_scheme IS 'Indicates whether scheme is "default", "none" or "custom".'
CREATE TABLE community_scheme ( comsc_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, com_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, com_scheme INT4 DEFAULT '0' NOT NULL, CONSTRAINT pk_community_scheme PRIMARY KEY(comsc_identifier) )
COMMENT ON TABLE community_scheme IS 'List of schemes for communities.'
COMMENT ON COLUMN community_scheme.comsc_identifier IS 'Unique Identifier for this community scheme.'
COMMENT ON COLUMN community_scheme.com_identifier IS 'Identifier of community'
COMMENT ON COLUMN community_scheme.com_scheme IS 'Indicates whether scheme is "default", "none" or "custom".'

CREATE TABLE subscriber_blocked_cats ( scrct_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, scr_identifier INT8 DEFAULT '0' NOT NULL, scr_category VARCHAR(128) NOT NULL, CONSTRAINT pk_subscriber_cats PRIMARY KEY(scrct_identifier) )
COMMENT ON TABLE subscriber_blocked_cats IS 'List of subscriber tied categories that are blocked.'
COMMENT ON COLUMN subscriber_blocked_cats.scrct_identifier IS 'Unique Identifier for this subscriber category.'
COMMENT ON COLUMN subscriber_blocked_cats.scr_identifier IS 'Identifier of subscriber.'
COMMENT ON COLUMN subscriber_blocked_cats.scr_category IS 'String name of category.'

CREATE TABLE community_blocked_cats ( comct_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, com_identifier INT8 DEFAULT '0' NOT NULL, com_category VARCHAR(128) NOT NULL, CONSTRAINT pk_community_blocked_cats PRIMARY KEY(comct_identifier) )

COMMENT ON COLUMN community_blocked_cats.comct_identifier IS 'Unique Identifier for this community category'
COMMENT ON COLUMN community_blocked_cats.com_identifier IS 'Identifier of community'
COMMENT ON COLUMN community_blocked_cats.com_category IS 'String name of category'

CREATE TABLE subscriber_services ( scrse_identifier INT8 NOT NULL, scr_identifier INT8 DEFAULT '0' NOT NULL, ss_target_type VARCHAR(128), ss_target_url_sc VARCHAR(128), ss_target_sc_keyword VARCHAR(128), ss_block BOOLEAN DEFAULT TRUE, CONSTRAINT pk_subscriber_services PRIMARY KEY(scrse_identifier) )

COMMENT ON COLUMN subscriber_services.ss_block IS 'Is this target specifically blocked or is an excpetion allowed?'
